com.intel.fightclub.dialog

Class UtteranceHelper

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.intel.fightclub.dialog.UtteranceHelper

  • @ThreadSafe
public final class UtteranceHelper
extends java.lang.Object
    Wraps and eases use of thread-safe UtteranceGeneratorManager. It offers several APIs for the UI to generate workout plan descriptions, definitions, etc.
